ol.li:
Configure Nginx to enable GZIP compression.
Sample configuration for Nginx to
                enable GZIP compression:server {
    ......             
    gzip on;
    gzip_types text/css text/javascript application/javascript text/xml text/plain application/json application/xml;
    gzip_proxied no-cache no-store private expired auth;
    gzip_min_length 1024;
    gzip_vary on;
    gzip_comp_level 5;
}           
